{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC02_OSK_110.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x18,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Fritz!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Sophie? What is it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Have you seen Oskar?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "No, I haven't seen him around here..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I see... I wonder where he went..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Did something happen?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Well, Oskar was supposed to look after the store, but he went somewhere..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "And so you're searching for him?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x24,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Yeah... I wonder why he slacks off so much..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I think I can understand how he feels, just a little."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Huh!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "In the past, I worried about many things. For example, whether I should use a sword or a spear in a battle."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I see... That's a little unexpected."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "At the time, I didn't know how I would turn out in the future. There were many things that I wanted to do."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "It was almost painful to do the same thing, or stay in the same place for too long..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Huh, so you had a time like that too?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Yeah... And I think Oskar feels the same way."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I don't know what he'll do in the future, but he must have something that he's engrossed in now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "That reminds me. The other day, he said he had something important to do, and asked me to do his work for him."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I can understand him after traveling with him several times, but he's unexpectedly earnest at heart."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x2e,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "He cherishes his store, but he left to do something else. It must be very important."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Something Oskar thinks is important... Maybe it would be plants?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Thank you, Fritz. I think I know where Oskar could have gone."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "That's good. Do your best to find him."
        }
    ]
}